OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain this evening. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fcloudy with patchy rain, most
OL,9,Fpersistent across the west. Fresh to
OL,10,Fstrong southerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FPatchy rain in the morning.
OL,13,FBecoming dry in the afternoon some
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells breaking
OL,15,Fthrough, more especially in the west.
OL,16,FA few evening showers in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
