OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday and Wednesday begin frosty but
OL,7,Fstay dry and sunny. Freshening
OL,8,Fsoutherly winds on Thursday with some
OL,9,Fpatchy rain.
